{"tid":664650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講個笑話：法律面前 人人平等","createTime":"2018-05-14T08:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T09:40:26.000Z","uid":5843,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9748017af921211f3c9f6c8f18bc9a2ad6ca196a","tid":664650,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"涉藏大麻草被控 退休警司女兒再求以簽保守行為了事<br />\n<br />\n退休前曾任新界北警區及九龍城警區指揮官的高級警司狄志堅，其女兒去年涉藏有大麻草被捕，被控藏毒罪。她曾兩度向律政司申請以簽保守行為處理本案但被拒，案件原定今日開審，辯方再指被告患有注意力不足過動症（ADHD），上周才首次收到來自被告學校的精神科醫生報告，會再去信向律政申請以簽保守行為處理，押後至下月26日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n現於美國麻省東北大學就讀二年級的被告狄曉晴（19歲），今由父親陪同出席聆訊，她涉於去年7月5日在上水中心商場OK便利店對開管有兩個膠袋，內裏分別有4.9及3.8克大麻草。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180514/58190389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F58190389&d=jP1xHi%2F8I8lBzWYhOTrsJ26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=207255e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F58190389&h=7ecf469d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180514/58190389</a>"},{"pid":"0a10fe9e5e99ec39e9288ee7555886cd29a00ab9","tid":664650,"uid":18279,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法律面前，窮人含撚</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f658863d7b11d623bab61b543a8a1a0fdbb8baa","tid":664650,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"比較想知呢度班道友既睇法"},{"pid":"6ea7a92ff9ed380081c5bfa65cd28062c15c9ced","tid":664650,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass